Title: 调用关系图
Describe: 跨模块责任交接和关键调用链。
------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS - SDK 构建调用链

[Description]
`create_deep_agent` 是 SDK 调用链的中心：它读取 profile 与 caller spec，再把 middleware、工具、schema 和 prompt 交给 LangChain `create_agent`。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "调用方代码" as Caller
participant "create_deep_agent" as Create
participant "resolve_model" as Model
participant "HarnessProfile" as Profile
participant "Backend" as Backend
participant "SubAgentMiddleware" as SubMW
participant "FilesystemMiddleware" as FsMW
participant "langchain.create_agent" as LC
participant "CompiledStateGraph" as Graph

Caller -> Create: model tools subagents backend options
Create -> Model: resolve_model
Model --> Create: BaseChatModel
Create -> Profile: _harness_profile_for_model
Profile --> Create: profile config
Create -> Backend: StateBackend when omitted
Create -> FsMW: file tools and permissions
Create -> SubMW: inline subagents when present
Create -> LC: model prompt tools middleware schema
LC --> Create: agent graph
Create -> Graph: with_config metadata
Graph --> Caller: runnable agent
@enduml

[Detail]
图从调用方进入 `create_deep_agent` 开始。`resolve_model` 与 `_harness_profile_for_model` 决定 provider 与 harness profile，`StateBackend` 是默认 backend。`FilesystemMiddleware` 是内置文件工具和权限规则的载体，`SubAgentMiddleware` 在存在同步子代理时注入 `task` tool。最后 `create_agent` 接收组装后的 `model`、`system_prompt`、`tools`、`middleware`、`state_schema` 和 `transformers`。证据集中在 `graph.py:517-829`，公开导出位于 `__init__.py:9-47`。

------------------------------------------------------------
[Example]
S06_CALL_RELATIONSHIPS - 部署 CLI 调用链

[Description]
部署调用链将命令解析、项目读取、payload 构建、API 调用和本地 state 更新分离，便于测试纯函数和隔离网络边界。

[UML]
@startuml
participant "cli_main" as Main
participant "execute_deploy_command" as Deploy
participant "Project.load" as ProjectLoad
participant "payload.py" as Payload
participant "resolve_referenced_servers" as MCP
participant "ApiClient" as Api
participant "State" as State

Main -> Deploy: args.command == deploy
Deploy -> ProjectLoad: root
ProjectLoad --> Deploy: Project
Deploy -> Payload: build_payload
Payload --> Deploy: create_payload
Deploy -> Payload: build_directory_files
Payload --> Deploy: directory_files
Deploy -> State: State.load
State --> Deploy: local state
Deploy -> MCP: resolve_referenced_servers
Deploy -> Api: patch_agent or create_agent
Deploy -> Api: commit_agent_directory
Deploy -> State: save agent_id revision
@enduml

[Detail]
`cli_main` 的命令分发见 `main.py:151-167`。`execute_deploy_command` 使用 lazy imports 降低启动成本，读取 project、payload 和 state 后才进入 API 边界。`Project.load` 是 I/O 入口；`payload.py` 是纯转换；`ApiClient` 是网络边界；`State.save` 保存部署结果。这个责任划分让 dry-run 可以在 `commands.py:164-177` 直接打印 payload，而不触发网络调用。
